dialogue.introduction: Admiral, I'm Tanikaze! I'll be in your care from now on.
dialogue.library_intro: Madam Tanikaze here! I was helpin' out Hiryuu during the Battle of Midway, damn enemy planes were dropping bombs on us like rain... Back then, C'mmander Katsumi was amazin' like seriously.
dialogue.secretary3: What's going on? Do you want "There there, a good boy"?
dialogue.secretaryidle: Eeeeeek! I'm bored anyway. Why not go somewhere to have a night battle?
dialogue.secretarymarried: Admiral, what's up? Are you tired?
dialogue.wedding: What a strange admiral you are to be interested in me, Tanikaze! Then, tell me how you get to love me from the beginning. Hehe, it's fine, the night is long, you know.
dialogue.show_players_score: A report is coming to you, Admiral!
dialogue.joining_a_fleet: Just leave it to Tanikaze! Sortie!
dialogue.supply: Eeeek! Thanks to it, I CON win!
dialogue.docking_moderate_damage: I love taking a bath... a bath...
dialogue.ship_construction: A new ship seems to be ready!
dialogue.return_from_sortie: The fleet has returned! Goood job!
dialogue.battle_start: Shelling and torpedo attack, now let's start!
dialogue.mvp: Even though you may not imagine it, I Tanikaze is very alert, right? Bombs can't hit me, I suppose!
dialogue.moderately_damaged: No kidding! Nobody wants to see a figure like this...
dialogue.sunk: Even I, Tanikaze can't avoid it... It can't be help. I dare... to be sunk, eek...
dialogue.new_year_2015: Happy New Year, Admiral! Our condition is only going to get better this year! It'll be fine!
dialogue.fall_2015: So summer is finally over. Kinda sad, isn't it? Meh, whatever. There's gonna be another summer next year after all.
dialogue.fall_event_2015: Haah! This is the showlight for Tanikaze! Come at me!
dialogue.christmas_2015: Ooh, it's Christmas? That's nice isn't it, Christmas! Eh... this "turkey" thing.... I wanna try eating it!
dialogue.end_of_year_2015: Kaa! It's already December, it came too fast. I've finished with the New Year's Eve cleaning. I'm looking forward to the Toshikosha Soba, nyan.
dialogue.setsubun_2016: Kaa! It's Setsubun! This is nifty. Who should I throw it at? Hamakaze? Ah!?
